questions.question:
设随机变量 $X$ 与 $Y$ 相互独立, 概率分布分别为
\begin{tabular}{c|cc}
\hline$X$ & 0 & 1 \\
\hline$p_i$ & $1 / 3$ & $2 / 3$ \\
\hline
\end{tabular}

和
\begin{tabular}{c|cc}
\hline$Y$ & 0 & 1 \\
\hline$p_i$ & $1 / 3$ & $2 / 3$ \\
\hline
\end{tabular}

则下列式子正确的是 ().

questions.analysis:
因为独立同分布, 故
$$
\begin{aligned}
& \begin{aligned}
P\{X=Y\} & =P\{X=-1, Y=-1\}+P\{X=1, Y=1\} \\
& =P\{X=-1\} P\{Y=-1\}+P\{X=1\} P\{Y=1\} \\
& =\frac{1}{16}+\frac{9}{16}=\frac{5}{8},
\end{aligned} \\
& P\{X=Y=-1\}=P\{X=-1, Y=-1\}=\frac{1}{16},
\end{aligned} \quad \begin{aligned}
& P\{X=-Y=1\}=P\{X=-1, Y=1\}+P\{X=1, Y=-1\}=\frac{3}{8} .
\end{aligned}
$$

由于 $X$ 与 $Y$ 相互独立, 所以 $P\{X=i, Y=j\}=P\{X=i\} P\{Y=j\} . Z=\min \{X, Y\}$ 可取 0,1 , 且
$$
\begin{aligned}
& P\{Z=1\}=P\{\min \{X, Y\}=1\}=p(1,1)=\frac{4^2}{5^2}, \\
& P\{Z=0\}=P\{\min \{X, Y\}=0\}=1-p(1,1)=1-\frac{4^2}{5^2},
\end{aligned}
$$

故 $Z=\min \{X, Y\}$ 的分布律为
\begin{tabular}{c|cc}
\hline Z & 0 & 1 \\
\hline$p_i$ & $9 / 25$ & $16 / 25$ \\
\hline
\end{tabular}
